				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">when i changed my database password right before making the sql changes (i hadn't read the forums here yet, and was just going off the install files),  for some reason it didn't change it in my config file.  so apparently the forum was trying to utilize the db with a bad password?  or something similar.  
<br />

<br />
so from my end,  it looked like the forum was working perfectly right up until the last step of the mod install,  and then suddenly the whole thing was dead.  so my first assumption was that the mod was the cause.
<br />

<br />
also, to note, this mod works great... i was clearing out 3 to 5 spam messages a day,  and since the install, there have been absolutely no spam messages on my board.  good job, and thanks again  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
